# PaalStack Conventions

Source: https://github.com/paalamugan/paalstack-react-ui

All UI imports from `@paalstack/react-ui`. Server-safe utilities from `@paalstack/react-ui/lib`.

```tsx
import { Button, Card, Form, Heading, Text, Badge } from '@paalstack/react-ui';
import { cn, logger, httpClient, dateIntl } from '@paalstack/react-ui/lib';
```

---

## Component Creation — Props API first

**Always use Props API (single component, props only). Use Composition API (`*Root` + sub-components) only when Props API cannot express the required layout.**

```tsx
// ✅ Props API — default
<Card
  header={{ title: 'Welcome back', description: 'Sign in to continue' }}
  headerClassName="text-center"
  titleProps={{ className: 'text-2xl font-bold' }}
  footer={<><Separator /><Text>Footer content</Text></>}
  footerClassName="flex-col gap-3"
>
  {children}
</Card>

// ❌ Composition API — only when Props API is insufficient
<CardRoot>
  <CardHeader><CardTitle>Title</CardTitle></CardHeader>
  <CardContent>{children}</CardContent>
</CardRoot>
```

**Props API components** (single tag, no sub-components needed):
`Alert` · `Avatar` · `Badge` · `Button` · `Calendar` · `Card` · `Carousel` · `Checkbox` · `Collapsible` · `Combobox` · `DatePicker` · `DateRangePicker` · `Dialog` · `Drawer` · `DropdownMenu` · `Empty` · `FileUpload` · `HoverCard` · `Input` · `InputGroup` · `InputOTP` · `Loading` · `MultiSelect` · `NavigationMenu` · `NumberInput` · `Pagination` · `Popover` · `Progress` · `RadioGroup` · `Resizable` · `ScrollArea` · `Select` · `Sheet` · `Skeleton` · `Slider` · `Switch` · `Tabs` · `Textarea` · `Toggle` · `ToggleGroup` · `Tooltip`

**Composition-API roots** (use only when slots need custom control):
`AccordionRoot` · `AlertDialogRoot` · `AlertRoot` · `AvatarRoot` · `ButtonGroupRoot` · `CardRoot` · `CarouselRoot` · `CheckboxRoot` · `CollapsibleRoot` · `ComboboxRoot` · `DialogRoot` · `DrawerRoot` · `DropdownMenuRoot` · `EmptyRoot` · `FileUploadRoot` · `HoverCardRoot` · `InputGroupRoot` · `MenubarRoot` · `NavigationMenuRoot` · `PaginationRoot` · `PopoverRoot` · `ProgressRoot` · `RadioGroupRoot` · `ResizablePanelGroup` · `SelectRoot` · `SheetRoot` · `TabsRoot` · `TooltipRoot`

### Card — Props API reference

| Prop | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `header={{ title, description }}` | Header content |
| `headerClassName` | Class on header wrapper |
| `titleProps` | Props forwarded to title (e.g. `className`) |
| `descriptionProps` | Props forwarded to description |
| `contentClassName` | Class on content wrapper |
| `footer` | Footer content (ReactNode) |
| `footerClassName` | Class on footer wrapper |
| `action` | Top-right action slot in the header |

